<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" 
	      xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">

    <Paragraph Style="{DynamicResource HeaderParagraphStyle}">
        Essential Report Viewer for WPF (Preview)
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph  FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14">
        Essential Report Viewer for WPF is a powerful control used for viewing reports defined in Microsoft's RDL format. It is native of WPF component and provides support for viewing RDL files based on both RDL2008 and RDL2008R2 specifications. It also supports both Server and Client-side reports.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph  FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14">
        The following are some of the key features of this component:
    </Paragraph>
    <List FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14">
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14">Supports various chart types, which includes Area, Bar, Column, Pie, Funnel, Radar, Line and so on.</Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14">Supports both Matrix and Table and also  single, and multi-level row grouping and column grouping.</Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14">Supports other common controls such as Textbox, Image, Rectangle, Line and both Circular and Linear Gauges.</Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
        <ListItem>
            <Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14">Supports report parameter and also provides the ability to customize the toolbar items for the look and feel of the control.</Paragraph>
        </ListItem>
    </List>


